### üîπ **Be verb-‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶®‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ß‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶∞‡ßÇ‡¶™ (Three main forms)**

| **Base Form** | **Past Form** | **Past Participle** |
|----------------|----------------|----------------------|
| be             | was / were     | been                 |

